Trust Advisor --> Trust Advisor will provide suggestions based on AWS best pratices
Trust Advisor 

Trust Advisor will give suggestions based on 
 - Cost Optimization
    . Days considered before giving suggestion is it will consider based on past 14 days
    . Ideal Load Balancer
    . UnderUtilized AWS EBS Volume
    . Unassociated Elastic IP
    . AWS RDS idle DB instance 
 - Performance
    . High Utilization of EC2 instances
    . EBS Provided IOPS(SSD) volume Attachment configuration
    .
 - Security
 - Fault tolerance
 - Service limits
 
 
